# Raw phone footage stays local — this is a public GitHub Pages repo, so
# anything committed here is served on the live site and bloats every clone.
# Ship the encoded derivatives (hero-loop.mp4, hero-poster.jpg), not the source.
*.MOV
*.mov

# Business files never reach a public repo — the retainer deal, reports, and
# notes live in ../prime-power-wash/ (the non-repo folder), not here. Blog
# posts ship as .html; a .md in this repo is always a mistake.
*.md
retainer*
reports/

# Phone originals. Jack's photos arrive as HEIC (often misnamed .webp and
# rotated with no EXIF tag). Browsers cannot render HEIC — always convert to
# real WebP and ship the derivative. Originals live in
# ../prime-power-wash/assets/source/, never here.
*.HEIC
*.heic
